$interpreted: Tica: Alright! Let the entrance exam for student Leah commence!
Leah: Huh? Didn't we say...
Tica: Without the proper Soul Energy, even if you make it to the entrance, you won't be able to get inside.
Tica: Why not test your abilities now?
Tica: Hehe, you happened to bring an item that's a perfect rune medium!
Leah: You talking about these eggs?
Tica: Yes! But let's start with the basics.
Tica: Close your eyes, and imagine the energy flowing within you. Let it gather in the palm of your hand.
Leah: Oh, I failed...
Tica: Don't rush. For starters, that was pretty impressive~

Tica: This is a Soul Energy canister! It stores Soul Energy
and comes in handy for sorcerers during combat!
Leah: Awesome!!
Tica: Soul Energy exists everywhere in the world!
Tica: But to channel it into power we can use, a rune pattern is inscribed on the top of a rune device that can automatically transform the Soul Energy.
Tica: That way, even humans without knowledge of runes can use it.
Leah: I see!
Tica: To use arcane magic without limitation, sorcerers must imagine themselves to be vessels for Soul Energy.
Tica: So when casting spells, the energy can be released however we wish.
Tica: Through the medium, imagine the energy forming the shape of an egg. Let's give it another try?
Leah: Did it work?
Tica: Not bad, you're quite talented. Let's take on a more advanced challenge!
Leah: Eh? I need more time!
Tica: Try again to defeat those prickear monkeys!
Leah: But I'm not familiar with gathering Soul Energy yet.
Tica: Hehe, don't fret~ I'll be here to help you.
Leah: Whoo, I actually did it!
Tica: Doesn't it feel great to succeed?
Tica: This is the Rune Academy's entrance. Try to infuse the energy onto this stone tablet!
Leah: OK! Here I go...
Leah: This-This is...
Tica: Wow, you've passed~ Welcome to Rune Academy!
Leah: Thank you Tica, thank you so much!
Tica: Remember to not tell the Headmaster I helped you cheat.
Leah: My lips are sealed!

OK! Here I go...
This-This is...

Thank you Tica, thank you so much!

My lips are sealed!
